OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FA 15-year-old girl has become the 13th
OL,7,Fperson to die after getting into
OL,8,Fdifficulty in open water during the
OL,9,Frecord-breaking May heatwave.
OL,11,FOver the past week 11 children and two
OL,12,Fadults have now died in open water
OL,13,Fincidents as temperatures soared above
OL,14,F30C in parts of the country around the
OL,15,FBank Holiday weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
