CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780272174
OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FIn the latest incident, the family of
OL,7,FChiedza Nyanjowa, from Cheshire,
OL,8,Fissued a statement thanking members of
OL,9,Fthe public who pulled the teenager
OL,10,Ffrom the water and those who called
OL,11,Ffor help.
OL,13,FChiedza, 15, was swimming on Formby
OL,14,FBeach on Bank Holiday Monday, when
OL,15,Femergency services were called due to
OL,16,Fconcerns for her safety.
OL,18,FShe was airlifted to Alder Hey
OL,19,FChildren's Hospital, where she passed
OL,20,Faway on Saturday May 30.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
