CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780272174
OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FA statement issued on behalf of
OL,7,FChiedza's family said: "Her family
OL,8,Fwould like to express their gratitude
OL,9,Fto everyone that helped Chiedza.
OL,11,F"Her family are glad that there were
OL,12,Fpeople around her to support her,
OL,13,Ftheir support shows that she was
OL,14,Floved. This is a difficult time for
OL,15,Fthe family, who would appreciate any
OL,16,Fform of prayer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
