PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780272174
OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,F"Her family describe her as a bubbly
OL,7,Fperson, she loved Christ and going to
OL,8,Fchurch. She loved cooking, she was a
OL,9,Fgiver and wanted to be nurse when she
OL,10,Fgrew up so she could give back.
OL,12,FShe will be greatly missed and
OL,13,Fremembered for her kind spirit."
OL,15,FIt comes after Police Scotland
OL,16,Fconfirmed on Friday that 16-year-old
OL,17,FCharlie Noble had died after getting
OL,18,Finto difficulty in the water at
OL,19,FBracklinn Falls, near Callander, on
OL,20,FThursday, May 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
