OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FHis death is not being treated as
OL,7,Fsuspicious and a report will be sent
OL,8,Fto the Procurator Fiscal, the force
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThames Valley Police confirmed on
OL,12,FThursday that 14-year-old Baltazar
OL,13,FL'Qui, a member of the local Timorese
OL,14,Fcommunity, died "after getting into
OL,15,Fdifficulty in the River Thames at
OL,16,FDonnington Bridge" on May 27.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
