OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FIn a statement on behalf his family,
OL,7,Fthe Oxford Timorese Community
OL,8,FAssociation said: "This has been a
OL,9,Fvery painful moment not only for the
OL,10,Ffamily, but also for the Timorese
OL,11,Fcommunity in Oxford and across the
OL,12,FUnited Kingdom.
OL,14,F"This tragedy is also a reminder to
OL,15,Fall families and communities about the
OL,16,Fimportance of child safety around
OL,17,Frivers and open water areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
