PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780272174
OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,F"We encourage parents and guardians to
OL,7,Fcontinue supervising children closely,
OL,8,Fespecially near rivers and dangerous
OL,9,Fareas."
OL,11,FThe body of another teenage boy was
OL,12,Ffound on Thursday in Kent after
OL,13,Femergency services were called to
OL,14,Freports of concerns for a swimmer in
OL,15,Fthe Galley Hill Road area of
OL,16,FSwanscombe on Wednesday afternoon.
OL,18,FThe boy's death is not being treated
OL,19,Fas suspicious at this time, Kent
OL,20,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
