OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FSo far, those reported to have died in
OL,7,Fwater incidents are:
OL,9,FOther bodies found include 12-year-old
OL,10,FJunior Slater, from Clayton-le-Woods,
OL,11,Fwho died in the River Ribble,
OL,12,FLancashire, on Tuesday after getting
OL,13,Finto difficulty while swimming with
OL,14,Ffriends.
OL,16,FIn a statement, his family paid
OL,17,Ftribute to "our little blue-eyed boy".
OL,19,F"He will be truly missed. He was the
OL,20,Flife and soul of our lives," they said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
