OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FHis body was retrieved by emergency
OL,7,Fservices at 7.50pm on Tuesday
OL,8,Ffollowing a large-scale search
OL,9,Foperation.
OL,11,FEarlier on Wednesday, the body of a
OL,12,Fteenage boy was recovered from Hawley
OL,13,FLake near Blackwater, in Hampshire,
OL,14,Fafter he was reported missing on
OL,15,FTuesday.
OL,17,FFormal identification has not yet
OL,18,Ftaken place, but Hampshire and Isle of
OL,19,FWight Police say the missing boy's
OL,20,Ffamily have been notified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
