OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FOn Friday the family of 17-year-old
OL,7,FDavid Tita Jr paid tribute after the
OL,8,Fteenager was found dead in the water
OL,9,Fin Pick Mere, a lake in Northwich,
OL,10,FCheshire.
OL,12,FHe was reported missing after he was
OL,13,Flast seen swimming in the water on
OL,14,FTuesday, May 26, and was found by
OL,15,Frescuers that evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
