OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FDyfed-Powys Police said on Wednesday
OL,7,Fthat a 72-year-old woman had died at
OL,8,FWest Angle Bay beach, in
OL,9,FPembrokeshire, Wales, after being
OL,10,Fpulled from the water around 3.15pm on
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,FThe death is not being treated as
OL,14,Fsuspicious, and next of kin have been
OL,15,Fmade aware, the police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
