OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FThe body of Muhammed Secka, 16, was
OL,7,Ffound at Rother Valley Country Park
OL,8,Fduring the early hours of Tuesday
OL,9,Fmorning, following reports of a
OL,10,Fmissing child seen entering the water
OL,11,Fbut not getting out.
OL,13,FThe incidents follow the death of 15-
OL,14,Fyear-old Declan Sawyer, whose body was
OL,15,Ffound in a Lincoln lake on Sunday
OL,16,Faround 10.25pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
