PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780272174
OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FDeclan's father Carl described him as
OL,7,F"a funny and outgoing young man who
OL,8,Floved fishing and football," as he
OL,9,Fcalled on families to take care of
OL,10,Ftheir children when near water.
OL,12,F"Please can all parents, friends and
OL,13,Ffamily make their children aware of
OL,14,Fthe dangers surrounding water."
OL,16,FA man in his 60s also died at Tregirls
OL,17,FBeach, near Padstow, on Monday after
OL,18,Fsuffering a cardiac arrest in the sea
OL,19,Fwhile trying to help family members
OL,20,Fwho had got into difficulty in the
OL,21,Fwater, Devon and Cornwall Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
