OL,3,CGirl, 15, becomes 13th person to die
OL,4,Cwater during record heatwave
OL,6,FTemperatures provisionally reached 35C
OL,7,Fat Heathrow and Kew Gardens in London,
OL,8,Fwhile Cardiff Bute Park recorded 32.9C.
